text: Tim Collins (born 2 October 1975) is a Bermudian equestrian. He competed in the individual eventing at the 2004 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1975 births Category:Living people Category:Bermudian male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Bermuda Category:Equestrians at the 2004 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
